{"tid":2118043,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【科技台】歐洲大空局第一個木星探測器JUICE在德國開始建造，預計後年發射升空","createTime":"2020-07-21T08:34:18.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-21T09:16:36.000Z","uid":120678,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"36bcc0434a8b311e91b3f364f11ad4161a278fb6","tid":2118043,"uid":120678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T08:34:18.000Z","msg":"新鮮出爐的短片介紹今次任務：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=UMeSyQwgOFM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DUMeSyQwgOFM&d=PhzZiar3PrZ%2B4r6hY23RjxAEDuEYyIgqOvZcTDxqS2A%3D&h=39149e6b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=UMeSyQwgOFM</a><br />\n<br />\nJUICE譯成中文叫「木星冰月衛星探測器」<br />\n今次係歐空局第一次外行星探測任務，亦都係美國以外第一次木星探測任務<br />\n預計2022年5-6月發射，由阿里安5 ECA火箭或阿里安64型火箭發射升空<br />\n計劃總預算15億歐元(133億港幣)，經多次引力彈射，航行7年到達木星<br />\n<br />\nJUICE探測器機體2020年7月開始在德國南部腓特烈港進行組裝的相片<br />\n<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/EcaRsEsXkAI1edH?format=jpg&amp;name=large\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FEcaRsEsXkAI1edH%3Fformat%3Djpg%26name%3Dlarge&h=10ed3a4e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0b7cc8e75ef485f4a33a7f52de66740f0da790f5","tid":2118043,"uid":79117,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T08:35:22.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a1872e30d00b3d3e4ffd1d7791a7ae26f8a9b854","tid":2118043,"uid":40267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T08:40:46.000Z","msg":"伊奧利亞計劃<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bfdbf893aa10c41604e5e01a03b898e3da508df4","tid":2118043,"uid":280648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T09:16:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}